  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流系统的模块关系图，核心是仓库管理，四个业务模块围绕它：车队管理、仓储管理、配送路线，还有一个也是车队管理但侧重不同。我想用菱形布局，中心是FilesCenter代表仓库核心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，WriterTop和ScholarLeft都是Logistics_FleetManagement？VisRight是Logistics_Warehouse，CodeBottom是Logistics_DeliveryRoute？但FilesCenter您也说是仓库，这和VisRight重复了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "VisRight",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，FilesCenter是核心仓储模块，VisRight是外围的仓储服务节点。功能层级不同，FilesCenter作为中心枢纽，其他四个模块都与它双向连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，菱形布局画好了，中心是FilesCenter，四个角分别是WriterTop、ScholarLeft、VisRight、CodeBottom，都做了双向箭头。现在需要加上跨模块的协同关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要加，形成交叉协同：ScholarLeft连WriterTop，WriterTop连CodeBottom，CodeBottom连VisRight，VisRight再连回WriterTop，形成一个业务闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScholarLeft",
        "WriterTop",
        "CodeBottom",
        "VisRight"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "交叉协同的四条边加好了。还有别的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScholarLeft",
        "WriterTop",
        "CodeBottom",
        "VisRight"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加一个AI调度模块，也是Logistics_DeliveryRoute，但它要单向辐射到四个业务模块，表示智能调度中心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI",
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
        "CodeBottom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "AI模块加好了，指向四个模块。样式方面，核心FilesCenter用深蓝色，四个业务模块用稍浅的蓝色，AI用暖色调区分，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AI",
